History of recognition. Described as a Santa Catalina Island endemic ( Rentz & Weissman 1981 ). Listed under
Aglaothorax in OSFO
for unspecified reasons (
Cigliano et al. 2020
).

Type material. The holotype male is in the CAS collection. Images of the holotype are available at OSFO (
Cigliano et al. 2020
).
